## 6) Quality Gates (Must Pass)
An item is only complete when all gates pass:
1. Acceptance criteria satisfied.
2. No lint/type/build failures in touched scope.
3. New/updated tests pass.
4. No unintended changes outside declared scope.
5. Documentation updated when behavior/config changes.
6. Verification evidence recorded.

---

## 7) Risk & Rollback Framework
For each medium/high risk item:
- Define blast radius.
- Add feature flag or safe-guard where possible.
- Prepare rollback command/commit strategy.
- Record pre/post state checks.

Rollback minimum:
- Revert commit(s) for item ID.
- Re-run validation matrix.
- Confirm production-safe state.

